name: TurboTax 2010 Tax Return
summary: Learn about .TAX2010 files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: NOTE: TAX2010 files store Federal and State tax return information for the 2010 tax year. Therefore, they are most commonly created during the 2011 calendar year.

description: Electronic tax return document created by TurboTax 2010, a United States tax preparation and filing application; contains 2010 tax forms and data entered by the user; can be validated and e-filed using the software once the tax data is complete.
